Some questions:

Death?

Fall instead of Feign Death.

2) Any "spare" mesh armor u guy wanna sell? (to me)
>>I do want some if you have extra <grins> You must be a monk ;-)

3) Whats the usual time U ppl play in EQ?
>>I clocked 7 hours on SAT, playing a barbarian and a human. Actaully, spent
most of the time talking about crap with people while fishing.

Ever noticed majority of us Singys are monks? Will be happy to have Entreri
the DarkElf with us. Still wonder who would play a female ogre...<Yikes, the
thought scares me...my lunch is comin' up my throat>

<Argh! Shucks, its all over my keyboard now>

Wilson
